            <h4 class="avatar-tiny"><a href="//beta.slashdot.org/~mjwx" class="author" title="author name and user ID">mjwx (966435) </a> | about 2 months ago | <a href="//beta.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=5496249&cid=47610941">(#47610941)</a></h4>
